longBusinessSummary: Advance Residence Investment Corporation is the largest residential J-REIT, investing in over 270 rental apartments located mostly in central Tokyo and in other major cities throughout Japan (AUM over 460 billion yen). ADR can be expected to have a stable dividend in the long-term and can be considered as a defensive J-REIT, based on the stable income from residential assets and with the largest dividend reserve among J-REITs.
